dc_title_s: France--west coast, L'Adour, port of Bayonne (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: modified facsimile copy of French chart 6536, 3rd ed., 1992. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. "From surveys made by SHOM in 1961 and 1963, with additions and corrections to 1992." "Copyright 1992 SHOM -- France." "Soundings in meters." Includes Source of hydrographic information diagram.
